ank\">https://twitter.com/MarshaBlackburn/status/1198773803976810496</a><br />\n<br />\n更加多嘅tweet請入bot搵<br />\n<br />\n（twitter戰線)國際都關注今次香港的區選<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1754022\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1754022</a>"},{"pid":"8faceb95c1667e9bf9a1cfd3fa921d037f6a17a3","tid":1754662,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T09:41:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"029a539f66f0275a14a0ec6c1e05f7276ee919c5","tid":1754662,"uid":321509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T09:43:18.000Z","msg":"輸咗唔認<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6eb59452226075abc926c51fdeade76f16813253","tid":1754662,"uid":72381,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T09:43:50.000Z","msg":"人民日報班傻鳩幾時產生左民意逆轉左既錯覺？<br />\n一直都無變何來逆轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe6a27498fa91746edd59a3167a4ab106e0a6fe4","tid":1754662,"uid":227271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T09:44:35.000Z","msg":"你地依家知道一車車老人院同廢老係邊個指使啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1293020a66fa0a5d4ce4ee24165f2e151d9a6264","tid":1754662,"uid":128202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T09:45:45.000Z","msg":"柒少陣啦 輸打䇔要"},{"pid":"d2bef5528248df10be665cbcea7964fec2f05df2","tid":1754662,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T09:45:52.000Z","msg":"賊喊捉賊"},{"pid":"0281637ece83e9cb8758916159e889e05ad7e3b6","tid":1754662,"uid":202426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T09:46:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12f6cbe13dcfd93632c8d1e4aa5a0867